# CS360-Project1 Harshveer Grewal
## Project 1 - Indivual Section
### 1. New e-Commerce site
Use incremental method because it allows early delivery of important features 
to users who can give feedback, and allows new optional fetaures for the website 
to be added later on.
### 2. Dental office site
Use RUP method because the website can use an agile methed to develop basic 
features first like showing users clinic hours, location, dental staff, and 
downloadable forums, but can then use a linear method later on to add 
appointment booking, automated text reminders, and issue discounts.
### 3. Nuclear Power Plant
Use Spiral method beacuse it focuses on risk analysis and allows for 
itertive changes for safety, along with through validation at each step.
### 4. Department of Transportation
Use waterfall method because the requirements are clearly defined in the 
100 page specification and beacuase a clear deadline is set requiring planning.
### 5. Reducing Traffic
Use Spiral method beacuse it focuses on risk analysis which is equired for software 
interacting with hardware, itertive changes for safety, along with prototyping.
### 6. Educational game
Use incremental method because the main game can be developed quickly, and more 
features can be added to the game overtime.
### 7. Global Health
Use incremental method to deliver early version to show progress and get more 
grants, also allowing early feedback for new features and changes that need to be made.
